headline: Northern Trust Asset Management Hires Director of Quantitative Solutions, Asia Pacific
summary: MELBOURNE, Australia, November 11, 2024--Northern Trust Asset Management (NTAM), a leading global investment management firm, has named Jan Rohof as Director of Quantitative Solutions, Asia Pacific (APAC), based in Melbourne.
